				        {"🧠 Behaviors - General", "General Chat", "No specific resource/plugin/action signals matched. General Q&A or conversational usage.", 16, 1628},
				
				        {"⚙️ Behavior Modifiers", "Active Creation Rate", "% of interactions where Copilot performed write/create/send actions. Active = creating value. Passive = consuming information.", 17, 1701},
