				        {"📈 Value Metrics", "Time Saved (Summarisation)", "Time saved on communication. Fed by: Email Drafting, Email Summarising, Teams Messaging. Proxy: emails drafted per user per week.", 18, 1801},
				        {"📈 Value Metrics", "Communication Effectiveness", "Time saved on meetings. Fed by: Meeting Prep, Meeting Scheduling. Proxy: meeting summaries generated vs meetings attended.", 18, 1802},
