				        {"📈 Value Metrics", "Faster Information Discovery", "Better access to information. Fed by: Web/Enterprise Searching, File Retrieval, PDF Analysis, SharePoint Access. Proxy: sources per session.", 18, 1804},
				        {"📈 Value Metrics", "Data-Driven Decision Support", "Data-driven decisions. Fed by: Data Querying, Spreadsheet Analysis. Proxy: queries executed per user per week.", 18, 1805},
